snippet.title: Premier Manager 97 gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Premier Manager 97, PC game produced by Gremlin Interactive in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/premier-manager-97/12335/
Playing the first part of a season as trainer for Cardiff City and doing not so bad..
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
PC Calcio 5 - https://youtu.be/iqo5qVl0uDo
Ultimate Soccer Manager 2 - https://youtu.be/thR2_H_lQQI
Ultimate Soccer Manager 98 - https://youtu.be/_gN3SoIuJ1s
